---
title: withdrawal_construction (osaka-blocks)
---
stateDiagram-v2
    direction TB

    [*] --> q_init : start
    q_init --> q_set_index : index = U64
    q_set_index --> q_set_validator : validator_index = U64
    q_set_validator --> q_set_address : address = Address
    q_set_address --> q_set_amount : amount = U256
    q_set_amount --> q_final : freeze(Withdrawal)
    q_final --> [*] : done

    note right of q_set_amount
        INV: Withdrawal is slotted_freezable
        (immutable after construction)
    end note

    note right of q_init
        INV: All four fields (index, validator_index,
        address, amount) must be set
    end note
